text: This is my spotlight slash photo light. I have it on a set of four so it's supposed to mimic a spotlight from above on all of the frames and I just like it because it's more of a warm lighting at the end of the day and it just feels relaxing. It kind of puts the lighting on the photo frames but then it's not too much in your face. It just kind of is a nice accent for the wall and for the photos.
